al portrait of Atrina floating in space among stars", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/cosmic-atrina-550e5ed644351dac.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/cosmic-atrina-550e5ed644351dac.html"}, {"alt": "A bream fish resting on a stony riverbed in clear water.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/resting-bream-on-riverbed-b5b095dad6f4abbf.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/resting-bream-on-riverbed-b5b095dad6f4abbf.html"}, {"alt": "A fantasy digital painting of a bream with glowing patterns in deep sea.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/bioluminescent-bream-dream-15e6d6fd19674aef.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/bioluminescent-bream-dream-15e6d6fd19674aef.html"}, {"alt": "Intense macro shot of a skink\u0027s eye and scale texture in monochrome.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/skink-eye-macro-8dab77a7957fe43b.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/skink-eye-macro-8dab77a7957fe43b.html"}, {"alt": "A skink adapted to desert life on sandy terrain.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/desert-skink-b92fa88fbff3efdb.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/desert-skink-b92fa88fbff3efdb.html"}, {"alt": "Dynamic action of a tamarin swinging.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/swinging-through-the-jungle-deb2d21232b93774.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/swinging-through-the-jungle-deb2d21232b93774.html"}, {"alt": "A tamarin family cuddled together on a branch.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/family-huddle-in-the-canopy-1af944fea4d99b1b.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/family-huddle-in-the-canopy-1af944fea4d99b1b.html"}, {"alt": "A minimalist line art drawing of a tilapia on white background.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/line-art-tilapia-634313ce0fb9c06f.jpg", "url": "/wallpapers/line-art-tilapia-634313ce0fb9c06f.html"}, {"alt": "A family of marmosets huddling together on a tree branch.", "thumb_url": "https://wallpapers.com/images/thumbnail/marmoset-family-on-branch-5ec7